      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "MONTY ZOOMER (4) led them up at this track last time out over 1617m when beaten in a photo finish as the race favourite. Back to 1400m now is no issue as he's raced well at this track and trip previously. Has the speed to get up front from the gate and he'll take plenty of catching. DONT WAIT FOR LUCK (1) got back to winning ways last time out when storming over the top over 1300m last time out. He was the favourite there and this looks to shape similarly with Martinan's claim coming in handy. Won 2/3 at this track and trip and can go back-to-back. PLAYING GAMES (7) finished off nicely behind Don't Wait For Luck last time out after settling well back in the run. Faithfull hops on board now and she can get back to winning ways. CELEBRITY PRINCE (3) was superb late in the race last start as a 30-1 chance and can't be left out of calculations. SURE THING (2) will give a bold sight from the front.",
